# D: reduplication
# |: separator following first character of n|saff, n|qsaqs, q|bTbT, x|kWrmm
# 1: possible glottal stop ending prefixed prepositions
# 3: 3sm object suffix
# 7: k/h subject suffix
# 8: palatalization

